The bug was found [here](https://discuss.elastic.co/t/es-7-10-ignores-analyzer-in-as-you-type-fields/256113)
and can be reproduced with:

```
PUT origin/

PUT origin/_mapping
{
    "properties": {
	    "url": {
	        "type": "text",
	        "analyzer": "simple",
	        "fields": {
	            "as_you_type": {
	                "type": "search_as_you_type",
	                "analyzer": "simple"
	            }
	        }
	    }
	}
}

POST origin/_doc/
{"url": "http://barbaz.qux"}

POST origin/_search?pretty
