```

The `edge_ngram` are not produced for the `search_as_you_type` field so the query doesn't match. I tested in 7.11-SNAPSHOT and it works as expected so it seems that it was inadvertently fixed. Although I am opening this issue to find the fix that we applied and to ensure that it is backported to 7.10.x.

